===============================================================
=========            COMPILATION OPTIONS              =========
===============================================================
In order to build modules for silenteye, set the following environnement variable to 1 :
ENABLE_MODULE=1

In order to build testsuites for silenteye, set the following environnement variable to 1 :
ENABLE_TESTSUITE=1

In order to build application and modules (plugins) in static mode :
ENABLE_STATIC=1

In order to enable "make install" command (also enable CPack) :
ENABLE_PACK=1

==========   Change default lib path   ==========
BINPATH_VALUE=/usr/bin
(install executable to /usr/bin/silenteye)

==========   Change default lib path   ==========
LIBPATH_VALUE=/usr/lib/silenteye/
(use /usr/lib/silenteye/libsef.so and /usr/lib/silenteye/modules/*.so)

==========   Change default configuration path   ==========
CONFPATH_VALUE=/etc/silenteye
(use /etc/silenteye/silenteye.conf and /etc/silenteye/version.xml)
or
CONFPATH_USERHOME=1
(use $HOME/.silenteye/silenteye.conf and $HOME/.silenteye/version.xml)

=========   Change default log path   ==========
LOGPATH_VALUE=/var/log/
(use /var/log/silenteye.log)
or
LOGPATH_USERHOME=1
(use $HOME/.silenteye/silenteye.log)

=========   Change default share path   ==========
CMNPATH_VALUE=/usr/share/silenteye/
(use /usr/share/silenteye/version.xml)

---------   Change default doc path (installation only)  ----------
DOCPATH_VALUE=/usr/share/doc

---------   Change default pixmaps path (installation only)  ----------
PIXPATH_VALUE=/usr/share/pixmaps

---------   Create gnome menu entry on install ----------
ENABLE_GNOMEMENU=1
(create /usr/share/applications/silenteye.desktop)

===============================================================
==========           INSTALLATION EXAMPLE            ==========
===============================================================
$root> ENABLE_PACK=1 ENABLE_MODULE=1 LOGPATH_USERHOME=1 CONFPATH_USERHOME=1 ENABLE_GNOMEMENU=1 cmake .
$root> make
$root> make install
or
$root> make install DESTDIR=$PKG
